Algorithm for preparing for work.

Check if my uniform has been washed.
    If false -> begin having uniform cleaned and continue
    If true -> continue
Check if I have showered.
    If false -> take a shower, then put on uniform
    If true -> put on uniform
Put on formal work shoes.
Brush my teeth.
Put phone, wallet and keys, into my pocket.
Put (cleaned) apron into bag.
Check that nametag is still in bag.
    If false -> find the nametag and put it into bag
    If true -> continue
Take headphones and put them in bag too.
Leave house to catch the bus.
Check hunger prior to work.
    If really hungry -> Buy food before entering work
    If hungry -> Enter work, but look into making a staff order during shift
    If not hungry -> Enter work